name: TC_01_02_01 | Verify successful registration of Free user
description: To verify that a Free user can successfully register.
descriptionHtml: To verify that a Free user can successfully register.

testStage.description: To verify that a Free user can successfully register.

steps.name: Navigate to the Free user registration page
Verify that the user is on the Confirm account page
Retrieve the confirmation link from the user's email.
Click the Settings on the Side Menu
Verify that the billing plan description is Free
